@startuml
actor User
participant "API Gateway" as API
participant "Intent Router (Agent 01)" as IR
participant "Response Orchestrator (Agent 02)" as RO
participant "Project Definition (Agent 08)" as A08
participant "Schedule & Planning (Agent 10)" as A10
participant "Connector Runtime" as CR
participant "Canonical Data" as Data

User -> API: "Create a new project for ERP rollout"
API -> IR: classify intent + context
IR -> RO: intent=create_project
RO -> A08: draft charter + scope
A08 -> Data: validate schema + store draft
RO -> A10: generate initial WBS
A10 -> CR: fetch resource availability
CR -> Data: sync resource data
A10 -> Data: store schedule baseline
RO -> API: compose response + next steps
API -> User: charter + baseline + approvals needed
@enduml
